  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.poster.avif?t=1721687851\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.webm?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.mp4?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CONTINUUM is an arcade FPS with rogue-like elements that puts the player in control of a synthetic avatar, tasked with completing combat simulations in an effort to gather data for a powerful and unknown intelligence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.poster.avif?t=1721687851\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.webm?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.mp4?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENHANCE YOUR COMBAT EFFECTIVENESS</h2>Your avatar is armed with a powerful cannon, modular in nature and capable of morphing into various offensive forms. Install a variety of augments throughout each run to increase the effectiveness of each morph, lest the avatar be overrun by hordes of simulated combatants.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTENDED ARSENAL</h2>Utilize arm-mounted equipment for even more ways to dispatch enemies. Explosives, traversal options, and more will carry you even further into the simulation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANNING AHEAD</h2>Discover Core Modules that alter various aspects of your avatars abilities. These Modules persist between simulations and can be modified at the beginning of any iteration.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.poster.avif?t=1721687851\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.webm?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/db14309910bd15fb6723761ebb5c5fba.mp4?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CONTINUUM is an arcade FPS with rogue-like elements that puts the player in control of a synthetic avatar, tasked with completing combat simulations in an effort to gather data for a powerful and unknown intelligence.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.poster.avif?t=1721687851\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.webm?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779150/extras/5a6c1ca1d7f8571c8e49e25f915fc218.mp4?t=1721687851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENHANCE YOUR COMBAT EFFECTIVENESS</h2>Your avatar is armed with a powerful cannon, modular in nature and capable of morphing into various offensive forms. Install a variety of augments throughout each run to increase the effectiveness of each morph, lest the avatar be overrun by hordes of simulated combatants.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTENDED ARSENAL</h2>Utilize arm-mounted equipment for even more ways to dispatch enemies. Explosives, traversal options, and more will carry you even further into the simulation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLANNING AHEAD</h2>Discover Core Modules that alter various aspects of your avatars abilities. These Modules persist between simulations and can be modified at the beginning of any iteration.",
